### ==========================================================
### 🔑 SETUP: AUTHENTICATION & TOKENS
### (املأ المتغيرات التالية بالبيانات الناتجة من الطلبات 1 و 2 و 6)
### ==========================================================

@user_email = user_api_test@example.com
@user_password = Password123
@user_token =
@artist_token =
@api_key =
@artist_id = 1
@song_id = 1


### 1. 👥 SIGN UP (USER) - Run this first
# Endpoint: POST /auth/signup
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{user_email}}",
  "password": "{{user_password}}",
  "firstName": "Auth",
  "lastName": "Test"
}

### 2. 🔑 LOGIN (GET JWT TOKEN) - Run this second
# ✅ SUCCESS: انسخ الـ accessToken وضعه في متغير @user_token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{user_email}}",
  "password": "{{user_password}}"
}


### ==========================================================
### 🧑‍💻 USERS MODULE (Testing CRUD & Serialization)
### ==========================================================

### 3. GET ALL USERS (Test Serialization)
# Endpoint: GET /users
# ✅ SUCCESS: يجب أن ينجح ويرجع بيانات المستخدم بدون حقل password أو apiKey.
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 4. GET USER BY ID
# Endpoint: GET /users/:id
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 5. UPDATE USER (PATCH)
# Endpoint: PATCH /users/:id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "firstName": "UpdatedFirstName"
}

### 6. DELETE USER
# Endpoint: DELETE /users/:id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### ==========================================================
### 🎶 ARTISTS MODULE (API Key Guard Test)
### ==========================================================

### 7. CREATE ARTIST (SETUP)
# Endpoint: POST /artists
# NOTE: يُفضل استخدام حماية JWT هنا، لكن نتركه مؤقتاً غير محمي في الكورس.
POST http://localhost:3000/artists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ezat Singer (ID: 1)"
}

### 8. GET ALL ARTISTS (FAIL without Key)
# Endpoint: GET /artists
# 🛑 FAILURE: يجب أن يفشل بـ 401 Unauthorized (لأنه لم يجد API Key)
GET http://localhost:3000/artists


### 9. GET ALL ARTISTS (Success with API Key)
# Endpoint: GET /artists
# ✅ SUCCESS: يجب أن تنجح بمجرد وضع الـ API Key الصحيح في متغير @api_key
GET http://localhost:3000/artists
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### 10. GET ARTIST BY ID
# Endpoint: GET /artists/:id
GET http://localhost:3000/artists/{{artist_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### 11. UPDATE ARTIST
# Endpoint: PATCH /artists/:id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/artists/{{artist_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

{
  "name": "Updated Artist Name"
}

### 12. DELETE ARTIST
# Endpoint: DELETE /artists/:id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/artists/{{artist_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}


### ==========================================================
### 🎧 SONGS MODULE (JWT & Roles Guard Test)
### ==========================================================

### 13. FAIL: Create Song (Unauthorized Role - User is USER)
# Endpoint: POST /songs
# 🛑 FAILURE: يجب أن يفشل بـ 403 Forbidden (لتأكيد عمل RolesGuard)
POST http://localhost:3000/songs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "title": "Unauthorized Song",
  "artistId": 1
}

### 14. GET ALL SONGS (Secured - Needs JWT)
# Endpoint: GET /songs
GET http://localhost:3000/songs
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 15. GET SONG BY ID
# Endpoint: GET /songs/:id
GET http://localhost:3000/songs/{{song_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### ==========================================================
### 🔐 TWO-FACTOR AUTHENTICATION (2FA)
### ==========================================================

### 16. GENERATE 2FA SECRET (QR Code)
# Endpoint: POST /auth/2fa/generate
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 17. TURN ON 2FA
# Endpoint: POST /auth/2fa/turn-on
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/turn-on
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "twoFactorCode": "123456"
}

### 18. AUTHENTICATE WITH 2FA
# Endpoint: POST /auth/2fa/authenticate
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "twoFactorCode": "123456"
}


### ==========================================================
### 🏥 APP HEALTH CHECK
### ==========================================================

### 19. APP HEALTH CHECK
# Endpoint: GET /
GET http://localhost:3000/

### ==========================================================
### 🔐 اختبار المصادقة الثنائية (2FA)
### ==========================================================

### 13. (2FA) توليد المفتاح السري والـ QR Code
# Endpoint: POST /auth/2fa/generate
# ✅ SUCCESS: سيعود لك المفتاح السري (twoFactorSecret) ورابط الـ QR
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 14. (2FA) تأكيد التفعيل (Turn-On)
# 🛑 النتيجة المتوقعة: 200 OK (إذا كان الكود صحيحًا)
# 💡 يجب إدخال كود فعلي من تطبيق Google Authenticator بعد عمل Scan للـ URL الناتج من الطلب 13.
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/turn-on
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "twoFactorCode": "123456" 
  // 🚨 ضع هنا الكود الحقيقي المولد من تطبيق Authenticator 🚨
}

### 15. (2FA) محاولة الدخول بعد التفعيل
# Endpoint: POST /auth/2fa/authenticate
# 🛑 النتيجة المتوقعة: 200 OK (لإتمام عملية اللوجن)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/2fa/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "twoFactorCode": "123456" // 🚨 ضع الكود الحقيقي هنا 🚨
}
